I"<p>
The purpose of this project was to bring the game Sims into a physical space and challenge the narrative of technology controlling our every actions. The command unit is controlled with an Arduino which gives the user actions to follow. Each LED is representatives individual “needs” the program is accounting for when weighing actions. If actions aren't completed within a specified timeframe, the health goes down. 
</p>
